thread.title: Katrina Perkins
thread.title_full: Frames Direct reviewed by Katrina Perkins

author: Katrina Perkins
title: Katrina Perkins
text: I ordered sunglasses on December 29th, 2016. I paid for overnight shipping which was $18.00. California came out of a drought, Megyn Kelley got a new show, property insurance rates rose and our new president has already taken a vacation, all before I received my sunglasses. I just want my very expensive sunglasses that I paid for.
